\end_inset

 would hover at closer to 20%, almost all bibliographic entries have full
 names attached to them.
 The missing N/A names are largely corporations, non-Anglo names, or solitary
 initials, and published long enough ago that no bibliographic database
 retains their full name.
\end_layout

